plot: Discussing the TikTok ban in the U.S.; Donald Trump's controversial nomination of Matt Gaetz to be Attorney General.

John Oliver discusses the most popular social media platform in TikTok's potential ban in the United States. He explains why US is focusing on TikTok where the same thing is being done by the US based companies even in a larger scale. Also he set up a days without incident clock until the return of the show for next season.—Niaz Islam Arif
